<TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Its not necesary to press "back" to stop..just release your run key and then start rotating.  The rotation alone will update the server with your new position/movement and prevent the the spell interrupt.  <P>Get in the habit of always rotating while casting to pull.  You'll be surprised at the adds you can avoid by rotating and aborting a cast if something snuck up behind ya.<P>Lyfe</FONT>
